my psychotherapy treatment.

515
00:40:41,100 --> 00:40:44,600
- I met him at the hospital.
- Did you?

516
00:40:49,400 --> 00:40:52,700
- You're here.
- Hello, Professor Ju.

517
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:54,200
Oh, I'm glad you found the way okay.

518
00:40:54,260 --> 00:40:56,960
- Are you okay to come out today?
- Yes.

519
00:40:57,030 --> 00:41:00,830
Even my doctor told me
to not stay home all day.

520
00:41:00,900 --> 00:41:02,900
He told me I should
practice walking a lot.

521
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:04,430
I didn't realize it at the hospital,

522
00:41:04,500 --> 00:41:07,000
