523
00:41:08,030 --> 00:41:09,460
I do?

524
00:41:10,330 --> 00:41:13,200
By the way, do you two
know each other?

525
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:17,900
Well, we know
each other a little bit.

526
00:41:18,300 --> 00:41:19,830
I see.

527
00:41:20,560 --> 00:41:22,400
- Then shall we go in?
- Sure.

528
00:41:22,930 --> 00:41:24,400
About my lecture today...

529
00:41:27,300 --> 00:41:30,030
- Hope you like the class.
- Thank you.

530
00:41:35,160 --> 00:41:38,630
- Bong-pal, hi.
- Hi, Seo-yeon.

531
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:41,360
