532
00:41:42,930 --> 00:41:47,060
- She's sitting in today.
- Ah.

533
00:41:47,130 --> 00:41:50,460
- Hello.
- Hello.

534
00:41:55,700 --> 00:41:57,560
She's just sitting in?

535
00:41:58,160 --> 00:42:00,200
Didn't he say
I was his girlfriend last time?

536
00:42:02,760 --> 00:42:04,300
Are you hurt?

537
00:42:04,360 --> 00:42:06,800
What happened? Are you hurt?

538
00:42:08,230 --> 00:42:09,700
