as toys, rocks, and plants...

549
00:42:50,730 --> 00:42:53,530
Lift it a bit higher.

550
00:42:53,600 --> 00:42:54,700
Higher.

551
00:42:55,530 --> 00:42:58,900
Tie it a bit tighter.

552
00:42:58,960 --> 00:43:00,430
Come on.

553
00:43:00,500 --> 00:43:03,260
Shall I pull it tighter?

554
00:43:06,700 --> 00:43:08,600
- You tied it?
- I did.

555
00:43:08,660 --> 00:43:10,700
Pull it now.

556
00:43:12,260 --> 00:43:15,800
Excuse me. What do you
think you're doing here?

557
00:43:15,860 --> 00:43:18,300
You can't be doing this, seriously.

558
00:43:18,360 --> 00:43:21,700
Did you get permission
from the police station?

559
00:43:21,760 --> 00:43:23,130
Are we supposed to get permission?

560
00:43:23,200 --> 00:43:26,400
- No.
- This is just too much.

561
00:43:26,460 --> 00:43:29,160
What's all this, huh?

562
00:43:31,160 --> 00:43:32,560
(Looking for a Witness!)

563
00:43:34,130 --> 00:43:35,800
Are there too many?

564
00:43:37,500 --> 00:43:40,130
Can you please try to investigate?

565
00:43:40,200 --> 00:43:43,000
How can I just take
your word and investigate?

566
00:43:43,060 --> 00:43:45,030
You will find something
only if you investigate.

567
00:43:45,100 --> 00:43:47,900
Ju Hye-sung, a veterinary professor
at Myongsung University.

568
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:50,500
- You will find something.
- Please leave.

569
00:43:50,560 --> 00:43:54,930
Conduct an investigation.
You will find something. Please!

570
00:43:55,560 --> 00:43:57,160
Hello.

571
00:43:58,760 --> 00:44:01,260
You're the detective
who released Bong-pal last time.

572
00:44:01,330 --> 00:44:04,260
- How are you?
- Hi.

573
00:44:04,330 --> 00:44:06,460
We've met before.

574
00:44:06,530 --> 00:44:08,760
