575
00:44:10,030 --> 00:44:11,560
(Ju Hye-sung, veterinary
professor at Myongsung University)

576
00:44:12,860 --> 00:44:16,160
How do you know Professor Ju?

577
00:44:16,230 --> 00:44:18,730
Do you also know him?

578
00:44:19,030 --> 00:44:22,000
