her belongings weren't found.

582
00:44:29,830 --> 00:44:31,860
It was because he took them all.

583
00:44:31,930 --> 00:44:34,630
Even so, without any evidence,
we can't start the investigation.

584
00:44:34,700 --> 00:44:36,600
You should head back for now.
We will be in touch.

585
00:44:36,660 --> 00:44:40,260
It's better to start
the investigation soon.

586
00:44:42,760 --> 00:44:44,560
Hello, detectives.

587
00:44:44,630 --> 00:44:45,930
What's with them?

588
00:44:46,000 --> 00:44:48,730
We got a call about them
hanging banners illegally.

589
00:44:48,800 --> 00:44:51,500
The vendors caught these students.

590
00:44:51,560 --> 00:44:54,260
They said they knew you
so I brought them here.

591
00:44:54,330 --> 00:44:56,260
Good work. You can go.

592
00:44:58,230 --> 00:45:01,230
A banner? What is it about?

593
00:45:01,300 --> 00:45:03,430
A hit-and-run case?

594
00:45:11,560 --> 00:45:13,500
Go home.

595
00:45:16,900 --> 00:45:19,300
This case is proceeding
in an interesting way.

596
00:45:19,730 --> 00:45:22,930
Go get the case file
from the transportation department.

597
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:24,630
Yes, sir.

598
00:45:29,200 --> 00:45:31,260
We'll get going then.

599
00:45:31,330 --> 00:45:32,860
Wait!

600
00:45:43,100 --> 00:45:44,860
Anything you want to tell us?

601
00:45:44,930 --> 00:45:47,130
You attend Myongsung, don't you?

602
00:45:49,300 --> 00:45:53,960
- You rude punks!
- Why are you doing this?

603
00:45:54,030 --> 00:45:58,100
- Do you know Professor Ju Hye-sung?
- Professor Ju Hye-sung?

604
00:45:58,930 --> 00:46:03,230
Ah, he's a veterinary professor
at our school.

605
00:46:03,300 --> 00:46:07,060
Then can I ask you to do me a favor?

606
00:46:11,400 --> 00:46:13,760
We'll wrap up here for today.
Thank you.

607
00:46:13,830 --> 00:46:16,330
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

608
00:46:20,900 --> 00:46:22,430
- Bong-pal.
- Hyun-ji.

609
00:46:23,100 --> 00:46:25,400
How did you like my class?
Did you like it?

610
00:46:25,460 --> 00:46:27,830
- Yes, I liked it.
- Did you?

611
00:46:27,900 --> 00:46:29,430
A lot of students were dozing off.

612
00:46:29,500 --> 00:46:31,900
Were they? I thought it was fun.

613
00:46:31,960 --> 00:46:33,600
I'm glad you liked it.

614
00:46:33,660 --> 00:46:35,860
If you're free now,
maybe we can go eat together?

615
00:46:35,930 --> 00:46:38,800
We can also schedule
our next appointment.

616
00:46:38,860 --> 00:46:41,560
Can we do that next time?
I just have things to do today.

617
00:46:41,630 --> 00:46:44,400
Do you? That's too bad.

618
00:46:44,460 --> 00:46:47,400
- I will call you then.
- Sure. Thank you.

619
00:46:50,360 --> 00:46:51,960
Professor Ju.

620
00:46:53,330 --> 00:46:57,260
Well, I have something
to talk to you about.

621
00:47:01,760 --> 00:47:04,730
You said you wanted to tell
me something. What is it?

622
00:47:04,800 --> 00:47:09,760
It is...
I'm graduating after this semester.

623
00:47:09,830 --> 00:47:14,460
So I won't have much
time to see you.

624
00:47:14,530 --> 00:47:16,430
That's why...

625
00:47:18,900 --> 00:47:20,760
Go on.

626
00:47:23,400 --> 00:47:26,430
I like you, Professor Ju.

627
00:47:26,500 --> 00:47:30,430
I've liked you ever since I met you.

628
00:47:32,330 --> 00:47:34,130
I'm sorry.

629
00:47:35,230 --> 00:47:38,860
I wonder if I led you on.

630
00:47:39,460 --> 00:47:43,400
If I acted inappropriately,
I apologize.

631
00:47:45,130 --> 00:47:49,200
No, I'm the one
who started liking you first…

632
00:47:50,030 --> 00:47:53,060
Thank you for the sentiment.

633
00:47:53,130 --> 00:47:54,830
Then.

634
00:47:57,800 --> 00:47:59,200
This.

635
00:48:17,130 --> 00:48:20,600
Hey, why did you leave
without saying anything?

636
00:48:21,900 --> 00:48:24,460
You were talking to Professor Ju.

637
00:48:29,630 --> 00:48:33,200
- Are you mad at me?
- No.

638
00:48:33,260 --> 00:48:35,500
- No?
- No.

639
00:48:50,260 --> 00:48:52,260
- Bong-pal.
- Yes?

640
00:48:52,330 --> 00:48:54,530
Have I been here before?

641
00:48:56,130 --> 00:48:58,730
I told you that
you followed me around.

642
00:48:58,800 --> 00:49:02,500
I still can't believe that,
but this place is familiar.

643
00:49:34,860 --> 00:49:37,630
Ah, I need to go now.

644
00:49:37,700 --> 00:49:39,960
- Where?
- To see my friends.

645
00:49:40,530 --> 00:49:42,860
- Your friends?
- Yes.

646
00:49:42,930 --> 00:49:45,960
Some of my high school friends
live in Seoul.

647
00:49:46,200 --> 00:49:49,830
They will help me take the GED.

648
00:49:49,900 --> 00:49:52,060
- Will they?
- Yes.

649
00:49:52,430 --> 00:49:54,900
I'm going to get really busy soon.

650
00:49:54,960 --> 00:49:56,960
After taking the GED, I'll need to
take my college entrance exams

651
00:49:57,030 --> 00:49:58,800
and find a job…

652
00:50:00,700 --> 00:50:02,660
Take it easy. Why rush?

653
00:50:02,730 --> 00:50:04,660
I'm five years behind
compared to everyone else.

654
00:50:04,730 --> 00:50:06,730
I will have to try
five times harder.

655
00:50:07,460 --> 00:50:09,800
I want to get my life back together.

656
00:50:09,860 --> 00:50:12,130
I lost so much all those years.

657
00:50:12,200 --> 00:50:14,360
There are a lot
of things I want to try.

658
00:50:21,600 --> 00:50:24,230
Hi, Min-ji. Are you here already?

659
00:50:24,300 --> 00:50:26,400
Okay. I will be right there.

660
00:50:27,660 --> 00:50:31,160
- Bong-pal, I need to go.
- Have fun.

661
00:50:31,230 --> 00:50:33,860
See you next time. I will text you.

662
00:50:37,760 --> 00:50:39,300
It will be difficult for you

663
00:50:39,360 --> 00:50:43,330
but I don't think it's a bad idea
for you to help her live a new life.

664
00:50:43,400 --> 00:50:45,230
In order for Hyun-ji to move on,

665
00:50:45,300 --> 00:50:47,760
you need to let go
of her hand first.

666
00:51:03,960 --> 00:51:05,960
Let's get together more often.

667
00:51:37,500 --> 00:51:39,300
Seo-yeon.

668
00:51:40,200 --> 00:51:42,960
Hi, Bong-pal.

669
00:51:53,100 --> 00:51:59,900
- Did something happen?
- No, no reason.

670
00:52:09,730 --> 00:52:11,300
Stop drinking. You've had enough.

671
00:52:11,360 --> 00:52:13,630
- I'm okay.
- Stop drinking.

672
00:52:13,700 --> 00:52:15,330
I'm okay.

673
00:52:16,830 --> 00:52:20,830
- I'm sorry.
- It's fine. I'm going to wash up…

674
00:52:29,430 --> 00:52:32,400
See you next time. Bye.

675
00:52:58,400 --> 00:53:00,000
(Pharmacy)

676
00:53:05,300 --> 00:53:08,730
(Hyun-ji)

677
00:53:12,100 --> 00:53:14,960
- Where are you?
- Hello?

678
00:53:18,260 --> 00:53:19,260
Hello?

679
00:53:20,260 --> 00:53:22,330
This is Bong-pal's cell phone.

680
00:53:25,800 --> 00:53:30,400
Seo-yeon, get up.
I will take you home.

681
00:53:32,830 --> 00:53:35,360
- Hyun-ji.
- Hello.

682
00:53:35,430 --> 00:53:38,760
Hello. There is a cab outside
that brought me here.

683
00:53:38,830 --> 00:53:40,860
Take that home.

684
00:53:41,500 --> 00:53:43,060
Let's go, Bong-pal.

685
00:53:51,400 --> 00:53:53,230
- What's with you?
- What do you mean?

686
00:53:53,300 --> 00:53:57,030
You said you liked me
and that you were my boyfriend.

687
00:53:57,960 --> 00:54:00,000
Then why do you keep
changing your mind?

688
00:54:00,060 --> 00:54:01,430
It bothers me.

689
00:54:01,500 --> 00:54:04,400
- It bothers you?
- Of course, it bothers me.

690
00:54:04,460 --> 00:54:06,760
- Really?
- Yes, it just bothers me.

691
00:54:06,830 --> 00:54:09,100
You being with another
girl bothers me.

692
00:54:09,160 --> 00:54:11,500
You're smiling?
How can you smile now?

693
00:54:11,560 --> 00:54:15,500
When a man loves a woman,
he should follow through.

694
00:54:15,560 --> 00:54:17,300
You shouldn't do this.

695
00:54:17,360 --> 00:54:18,960
Even if I don't remember you,

696
00:54:19,030 --> 00:54:21,800
you should find a way
and try anything...

697
00:54:29,200 --> 00:54:30,900
You pervert!

698
00:54:31,430 --> 00:54:33,860
Don't ever call me again!

699
00:54:41,300 --> 00:54:43,500
Hey.

700
00:54:44,330 --> 00:54:46,560
You should at least apply
the ointment before you leave...

701
00:54:55,860 --> 00:54:58,360
I can't believe you asked
me to apply the ointment.

702
00:54:58,430 --> 00:55:01,100
